Persistence of Vision Raytracer Version 2.0
--------------------------------------------
These are the level 2 example scene files for use with the Persistence
of Vision Raytracer version 2.0.

To use the POV-Ray ray tracer, you also need POVDOC.ZIP for documentation,
and an executable for your computer. See the file POVINFO.TXT for
more information.

These files should be available from the same source from where
you received this file.
------------------------------------------------------------------------


Files contained in LEVEL2 sub-directory
---------------------------------------
ARCHES.POV    <- Arches standing in water - an Aquatic McDonalds?
CLUSTER.POV   <- A cluster of mirrored spheres - classic test scene
CRYSTAL.POV   <- A Crystal Ball on a Checkerboard - classic IOR test
EIGHT.POV     <- Behind the 8-Ball!
HFCLIP.POV    <- Height Field Clipped (Fractured) dowel
IORTEST.POV   <- IOR Test
LAMPPOST.POV  <- Old fashioned lamppost on a reflective floor
MAGGLASS.POV  <- Magnifying Glass
MTMAND.PAR    <- FRACTINT Parameter file for MTMAND Fractal
MTMAND.POV    <- Mount Mandelbrot! - 3-D Mandelscape
PACMAN.POV    <- Our Hero!  Pac-Man doing what he does best!
PAWNS.POV     <- Three pawns on a chessboard - wood study
PLANET.POV    <- So this is how they do the STNG title scenes!
POLYWOOD.POV  <- Wooden Polyhedron CSG on a grassy hill
POOLBALL.INC  <- Include file for POOLBALL.POV
